headline: Citi sets PT on Palo Alto Networks to $216 after stock split
summary: Investing.com -- Citi has reaffirmed its "buy" rating on Palo Alto Networks Inc (NASDAQ:PANW), adjusted its price target to $216 following the company’s stock split. The brokerage highlighted sustained growth prospects and a stable pricing environment as key positives.
